      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(cron): preserve enabled-with-defaults failureAlert across store round trips",
        "body": "Fixes #96589\n\n## 问题\n\n给 cron job 开了 `--failure-alert`（不带其他参数），gateway 重启后配置就丢了。`bindFailureAlertColumns` 把 `{}` 写成 `failure_alert_disabled=0` + 全部 null，但 `failureAlertFromRow` 读到全 null 时返回 `undefined`，系统以为没配 alert。\n\n## 改动\n\n`src/cron/store/failure-alert-codec.ts`，`failureAlertFromRow` 里全 null + `failure_alert_disabled=0` 时返回 `{}`（启用+默认值）而不是 `undefined`。\n\n## 序列化验证\n\n4 种配置的读写一致性测试：\n\n```\n=== cron failureAlert 序列化/反序列化测试 ===\n\n1. 启用+默认参数（--failure-alert 不带参数）\n   bind({})             → {\"failure_alert_disabled\":0, ...全部null}\n   failureAlertFromRow  → {}  (修前: undefined → 重启后丢配置; 修后: {} → 正确恢复)\n\n2. 显式禁用\n   bind(false)          → {\"failure_alert_disabled\":1, ...全部null}\n   failureAlertFromRow  → false\n\n3. 自定义参数（--failure-alert --failure-alert-channel slack --failure-alert-to dev-team）\n   bind({after:5,channel:\"slack\",to:\"dev-team\"})\n     → {\"failure_alert_disabled\":0, \"failure_alert_after\":5, \"failure_alert_channel\":\"slack\", \"failure_alert_to\":\"dev-team\", ...}\n   failureAlertFromRow  → {\"after\":5, \"channel\":\"slack\", \"to\":\"dev-team\"}\n\n4. 不配置（undefined）\n   bind(undefined)      → {\"failure_alert_disabled\":null, ...全部null}\n   failureAlertFromRow  → 按调用方逻辑处理，不影响\n```\n\n关键在第 1 组：修前 `failureAlertFromRow` 返回 `undefined`，重启后配置丢失；修后返回 `{}`，重启后配置正常恢复。\n\n## 改动量\n\n1 文件，+3 / -1 行。锁文件未变动。",
        "branch": "fix/issue-96589-cron-failure-alert-persist",
